         gst-plugins-base-libs lib32-gst-plugins-base-libs vulkan-icd-loader lib32-vulkan-icd-loader
         bottles cups dosbox glfw lib32-opencl-icd-loader lib32-vkd3d lutris opencl-icd-loader samba
